snippet.textDisplay: Seeing this game on many GOTY lists made me curious and when I saw it was a free visual novel on Steam, I knew something was up. Without reading anything on it, I played it recently and now understand the buzz. It's definitely not what it looks like. Watching the Game Theory videos about this game afterwards opened my eyes even more and is what confirmed that I needed to put it in my Top 10. I won't say anything more!
